# New Prisma Model — Workflow (ProjectFlo)

- Design schema in `packages/backend/prisma/schema.prisma`:
  - snake_case tables/columns
  - tenant scoping via a relation path to `brands` (or document intentional global scope)
  - `created_at` + `updated_at` on all models
  - indexes on FKs and expected query filters/sorts
  - use `Decimal` for money/percentages
- Generate client: `pnpm db:generate`.
- Create migration for production-bound models (don’t rely on `db:push` as final state).
- Implement backend module under the correct bucket (`platform|catalog|workflow|content|finance`) with controller/service/DTOs/README; filter by brand in services, not controllers.
- DTOs use `class-validator`; apply `ValidationPipe`.
- Routes start with `/api/*`, guarded with JWT.
- Add seed data only if needed; follow seed conventions and register in orchestrators.
- Add frontend feature API bindings in `features/<bucket>/<feature>/api/` using the shared `ApiClient`; add types under the feature `types/` (never `src/lib/types`).
- Add React Query hooks + query keys for server state consumers; brand-scope query keys and invalidation.
- Write/update the feature/module `README.md` to document the new source of truth.

